{"tid":1478692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂鬼 係指警方既臥底","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:47:11.000Z","uid":57614,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"504d605e98262285814b9d95649d42f54028c3d5","tid":1478692,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"鬼係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警方既臥底</strong></span> 唔係企出黎既香港人<br />\n大家唔知仲記唔記得 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不分化 不割蓆 不督灰</strong></span><br />\n正正兩個月以黎 我地無掛住捉鬼 唔割蓆 一齊團結先走到咁耐<br />\n你要捉既係臥底 唔係前線勇武或其他人<br />\n臥底係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔會亂幫你企前線同做抗爭行為</strong></span>  因為佢地都有生命危險 隨時中槍<br />\n臥底係會打同捉落單既人 銅鑼灣一事就睇到<br />\n請大家唔好再話捉鬼 鬼 兩個月以黎都存在 捉鬼係捉唔晒 捉鬼會捉著自己人"},{"pid":"6af4b97bb3d3737a750447bf55b0f199b3aab665","tid":1478692,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad94ec347ca0048f5bc0467e02b99852cf81fe61","tid":1478692,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"有無人認同"},{"pid":"95986ff16d764a4665498575197d175e33ff65ae","tid":1478692,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"無人理 由佢沉"},{"pid":"b8b04daccaba67cc453cf59f6175ebeda92f7b11","tid":1478692,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"韭菜花革命 中國正式啟動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033fb6f5f368c56b00faf429265911d3ddbff540","tid":1478692,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"公安、解放軍、藍絲多數都會混入"},{"pid":"35a340e90f5fd7955f5e12140b33babb4f373eae","tid":1478692,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy